NG0277:1: nub phyogs klu yi 'jig rten rab 'byams nas //
NG0277:2: 'gro ba'i tshe srog sdud ma klu yi rigs //
NG0277:3: kha dog me ltar 'bar ba'i mdog can ni //
NG0277:4: thugs rjes klog byed mkhor lo bsnams pa ni //
NG0277:5: klu yi gnas nas tshe drongs pho nya tshe mchog ma //
NG0277:6: na ga ba ru na ye tshe b+h+rum b+h+rum //
NG0277:7: rlung lha phyogs skyong la gnas tshe 'gugs ma //
NG0277:8: khro mo sku mdog sngo skya thal ba'i mdog /
NG0277:9: rdo rje rgyal mtshan lag na 'phyar ba'i mchog /
NG0277:10: rlung lha'i khyim ni rdul du brlag nas kyang *//
NG0277:11: rlung lha 'khor bcas lag nas tshe drongs shig / ba ya be tshe b+h+rum b+h+rum /
NG0277:12: byang phyogs gnod sbyin lag nas tshe 'gugs ma //
NG0277:13: kha dog ljang gu 'bar ba'i sku mdog la //
NG0277:14: ral gri ut+pal 'dra drangs nas kyang *//
NG0277:15: gnod sbyin 'khor bcas lag nas tshe drongs shig / ku+u be ra ba tshe b+h+rum b+h+rum /
NG0277:16: bgegs kyi rgyal po'i lag nas tshe 'gugs ma //
NG0277:17: mdog ldan sna tshogs kha dog ljang gu'i rigs //
NG0277:18: dbu mang spyan can rdzu 'phrul gdug pa'i phyag / rin chen mtshon cha sna tshogs dril nas ni //
NG0277:19: bgegs kyi khyim rnams thal bar brlag nas kyang *//
NG0277:20: bi na ya ga'i lag nas tshe khug cig / bi na ya ka nan tshe b+h+rum b+h+rum /
NG0277:21: nyi zla gza' skar lag nas tshe 'gugs ma //
NG0277:22: kha dog dmar ljang nyi zla'i 'khor lo 'phen //
NG0277:23: nyi ma'i khyim dang zla ba'i gnas rnams dang *//
NG0277:24: nyi zla gza' skar lag nas tshe khug cig / sur+ya tsan+d+ra ya tshe b+h+rum b+h+rum /
NG0277:25: sa 'og sa 'dzin lag nas tshe 'gugs ma //
NG0277:26: ye shes ting 'dzin lhag pa'i spu gri yis //
NG0277:27: phyag mtshan spu gri bsnams pas tshe khug cig / na ga pra we sha ya tshe b+h+rum b+h+rum /
NG0277:28: muk+ta ho yis bshig pas rdo rje gyur //
NG0277:29: rdo rje nyi zla rgya gram gyis //
NG0277:30: nr-i la bstim nas sba bar bya'o //
NG0277:31: om pad+man+ta kr-i ta h+ya gri wa e ka dza ti hu lu hu lu hu~m b+h+yo hu~m /
NG0277:32: ta kr-ita dmar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa //
NG0277:33: karma rgya gram bsnams nas yum dang 'khril //
NG0277:34: a ka tsa ti kha t+wam thod pa bsnams //
NG0277:35: thugs kar tshe dbang bsdus nas bsrung ba yis //
NG0277:36: stong pa'i dbyings su tshe sbas nas //
NG0277:37: chos kyi dbyings nas ye shes gsal //
NG0277:39: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa 'chi med tshe'i rgyud las /
NG0277:40: tshe gzhan gyi kha skong gi le'u ste brgyad pa'o
NG0277:41: // // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis tshe'i cho
NG0277:42: ga kun la 'gro ba 'di gsungs so //
NG0277:43: tshe bsgrub kha bskang nyin cig pa'am //
NG0277:44: gang yang rung ba'i bya ba ni //
NG0277:45: bum pa chang bkang tshe zan bca' //
NG0277:46: mda' dar dmar po me long thogs //
NG0277:47: rigs lnga so so'i snying po'am //
NG0277:48: spyi bsdus bgrangs la tshe bum bstim //
NG0277:49: de nas tshe ni dgug par bya //
NG0277:52: a pa ri mi ta a yur+dz+nyan /
NG0277:53: sam+b+ha ro pa tsi ta swa ha /
NG0277:54: hu~m bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NG0277:55: sgrib pa'i dri ma ma lus sel //
NG0277:56: mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sku mnga' ba //
NG0277:57: mnyam nyid sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0277:60: gsung mchog rnam par dag pa'i gsung *//
NG0277:61: mnyam nyid gsung la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0277:62: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NG0277:63: thugs mchog rnam par mi rtog thugs //
NG0277:64: mkha' dang mnyam pa'i thugs mnga' ba //
NG0277:65: mnyam nyid thugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0277:66: om b+hu d+d+ha lo tsa na a yu she om /
NG0277:67: badzra lo tsa na yu she hu~m /
NG0277:68: rat+na lo tsa na a yu she swa /
NG0277:69: pad+ma lo tsa na a yu she hrih /
NG0277:70: karma lo tsa na a yu she a /
NG0277:71: hu~m nam mkha'i dbyings phyug ma ni ye nas rnam
NG0277:72: par dag / rdo rje dbyings phyug ma ni ye
NG0277:74: rin chen dbyings phyug ma ni dgos 'dod re ba skongs //
NG0277:75: pad+ma dbyings phyug ma ni 'dzin med chags dang bral //
NG0277:76: las kyi dbyings phyug ma ni mngon spyod phrin las mdzod //
NG0277:77: dbyings phyug chen mo lnga rnams kyis //
NG0277:78: rdo rje tshe yi dngos grub stsol //
NG0277:79: om badzra a yu she a /
NG0277:80: hu~m shar gyi phyogs nas tshe 'gugs ma //
NG0277:81: gsang ba'i lha mo rgyas 'debs ma //
NG0277:82: rigs kyi lha mo sangs rgyas spyan //
NG0277:83: phyag rgya'i lha mo la s+ya ma //
NG0277:84: mchod pa'i lha mo d+hu pe ma //
NG0277:85: 'gugs pa'i lha mo lcags kyu ma //
NG0277:86: tshe bdag chen mo khyed rnams kyis //
NG0277:87: shar phyogs dri za'i lag nas tshe drongs la //
NG0277:88: shar lho me lha'i lag nas dpal skyobs shig / badzra am ku sha dzah /
NG0277:89: lho yi phyogs nas tshe 'gugs ma //
NG0277:90: gsang ba'i lha mo za byed ma //
NG0277:91: rigs kyi lha mo ma ma ki /
NG0277:92: phyag rgya'i lha mo ma le ma //
NG0277:93: mchod pa'i lha mo push+pe ma //
NG0277:94: 'ching ba'i lha mo zhags pa ma //
NG0277:95: tshe bdag chen mo khyed rnams kyis //
NG0277:96: lho phyogs gshin rje'i lag na tshe drongs shig /
NG0277:97: lho nub srin po'i lag nas dpal skyobs shig /
NG0277:99: nub kyi phyogs nas tshe 'gugs ma //
NG0277:100: gsang ba'i lha mo tshe 'phel ma //
NG0277:101: rigs kyi lha mo gos dkar mo //
NG0277:102: phyag rgya'i lha mo girti ma //
NG0277:103: mchod pa'i lha mo a lo ke //
NG0277:104: sdom pa'i lha mo lcags sgrog ma //
NG0277:105: tshe bdag chen mo khyed rnams kyis //
NG0277:106: nub phyogs klu dbang lag nas tshe drongs la //
NG0277:107: nub byang rlung lha'i lag nas dpal skyobs shig / pad+ma s+phot bam /
NG0277:108: byang gi phyogs nas tshe 'gugs ma //
NG0277:109: gsang ba'i lha mo rmongs byed ma //
NG0277:110: rigs kyi lha mo dam tshig sgrol //
NG0277:111: phyag rgya'i lha mo nirti ma //
NG0277:112: mchod pa'i lha mo g+han+d+he ma //
NG0277:113: 'bebs pa'i lha mo dril bu ma //
NG0277:114: tshe bdag chen mo khyed rnams kyis //
NG0277:115: byang phyogs gnod sbyin lag nas tshe drongs la //
NG0277:116: byang shar dbang ldan lag nas dpal skyobs shig / karma g+han+de ho /
NG0277:117: de nas tshe gzhan du yar ba dang */
NG0277:119: ldeg pa rnams bkug nas bum par bstim pa ni /
NG0277:120: hu~m a yur+dz+nya na tshe yi mchog / sa la nyams na gser la bsdu //
NG0277:121: chu la nyams na chang la bsdu //
NG0277:122: shing la nyams na mar la bsdu //
NG0277:123: rtsi la nyams na sbrang la bsdu //
NG0277:124: 'bru la nyams na til la bsdu //
NG0277:125: 'bru sna snying po sna lnga yis //
NG0277:126: sna lnga dag tu byin gyis rlobs //
NG0277:129: rdo rje tshe yi dbang bskur te //
NG0277:130: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NG0277:131: nam mkha' gsang ba gsum las byung *//
NG0277:132: nam mkha'i rigs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NG0277:133: dbang bskur chen po dam pa sbyin //
NG0277:134: om b+hud+d+ha ka la sha om /
NG0277:135: bud+d+ha lo can a b+hi shiny+tsa a+om /
NG0277:136: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NG0277:137: rdo rje gsang ba gsum las byung *//
NG0277:138: rdo rje rigs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NG0277:139: dbang bskur chen po dam pa sbyin //
NG0277:140: hu~m badzra ka la sha hu~m /
NG0277:141: badzra lo tsa na a b+hi shiny+tsa hu~m /
NG0277:142: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NG0277:143: rin chen gsang ba gsum las byung *//
NG0277:144: rin chen rigs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NG0277:145: dbang bskur chen po dam pa sbyin //
NG0277:146: swa rat+na ka la sha swa /
NG0277:147: rat+na lo tsa na a b+hi shiny+tsa tram /
NG0277:148: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NG0277:149: pad+ma gsang ba gsum las byung *//
NG0277:150: pad+ma rigs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NG0277:151: dbang mchog chen po dam pa sbyin //
NG0277:152: am pad+ma ka la sha hri /
NG0277:153: pad+ma lo tsa na a b+hi shiny+tsa hri /
NG0277:154: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NG0277:155: las rab gsang ba gsum las byung *//
NG0277:156: las kyi rigs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NG0277:157: dbang mchog chen po dam pa sbyin //
NG0277:158: ha karma ka la sha / ha karma lo tsa na a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NG0277:160: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa 'chi med tshe'i rgyud las /
NG0277:161: tshe bsgrub chen po byed rung */
NG0277:163: tshe chog nyin gcig pa byed rung */
NG0277:164: gang dgos su bstan pa'i le'u ste dgu pa'o ///
NG0277:165: / de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis longs spyod tshogs kyi sgrub pa 'di gsungs so //
NG0277:166: longs spyod bsgrub pa'i gzhi chen ni //
NG0277:167: gsang ba dag pa'i dkyil 'khor yin //
NG0277:168: longs spyod rgyu rtags phun sum tshogs //
NG0277:169: dkyil 'khor tshe bcas bkod pa dang *//
NG0277:170: gzhal yas khang dang tshe bskyed dang *//
NG0277:171: spyan drang dang ni bstim pa dang *//
NG0277:172: tshe yi rang bzhin 'gugs pa'i thabs //
NG0277:173: tshe bcings bzlas brjod tshe brlan dang *//
NG0277:174: dbang bskur sdom dang sba bar bya //
NG0277:175: dam bca' dor na bgegs dbang 'gyur //
NG0277:177: rbod gtong khar bab dus min 'gro //
NG0277:178: tshe nyams pa yi rgyu ru bshad //
NG0277:179: gzi brjid me dang lus nyams bral //
NG0277:180: mdog skya bya ba dor ba dang *//
NG0277:181: yid mi bde dang brjid stobs med //
NG0277:182: tshe nyams pa yi rtags su bshad //
NG0277:183: ston pa rgyu dang man ngag mkhas //
NG0277:184: gnas ni bkra shis nyams kyang dga' //
NG0277:186: yo byad rdzas rnams tshogs pa dang *//
NG0277:187: bkra shis dus la 'jug par bya //
NG0277:188: phyi mtshams dang ni phyi bshags dang *//
NG0277:189: nang mtshams dang ni kha skong bya //
NG0277:190: dam sri mnan dang sgo byang gdags //
NG0277:191: ma tram mnan cing rdo rje'i 'gros //
NG0277:192: mtshon cha khro bo khrag 'thung rol //
NG0277:193: bdag gi tshe yi sngon 'gror bshad //
NG0277:194: dkyil 'khor thig bzhi ling tshe dgu //
NG0277:196: sgo dang bcas pa bri bar bya //
NG0277:197: dbus su shel gyi bum par ni //
NG0277:200: cong zhi dkar po rnam gsum dang *//
NG0277:201: dkar dang mngar gsum 'chi med sman //
NG0277:202: byang chub sems sogs gzhag par bya //
NG0277:203: mu ge sel ba'i 'bru lnga dang *//
NG0277:204: 'du ba sel ba'i sman lnga dang *//
NG0277:205: nor gyi dbyig ldan rin chen lnga //
NG0277:206: snying po lnga dang dri lnga bshams //
NG0277:207: tshe 'bras rgya gram rgyas btab nas //
NG0277:208: mda' dang bcas pa bzhag pa ni //
NG0277:209: lha yi grangs dang mnyam par bya //
NG0277:210: mchod pa mang pos yongs su bskor //
NG0277:211: rtags gdab las ni bskos la gdab //
NG0277:212: rtags dang byin dbab bskang ba la //
NG0277:213: ting 'dzin gsum las byung ba yi //
NG0277:214: 'byung ba rim brtsegs gzhal yas gdan //
NG0277:215: dbus su tshe dpag med pa yab yum gnyis //
NG0277:216: phyogs bzhir rigs kyi yum bzhi la //
NG0277:217: mtshams su gsang ba'i yum bzhi nyid //
NG0277:218: pad+ma brgyad la lha mo brgyad //
NG0277:219: sgo bzhi sgo ma bkod nas ni //
NG0277:220: spyan drangs pa yi rim pa bya //
NG0277:221: tshe yi rang bzhin yum gyi mkha' //
NG0277:222: rdo rje rgya gram nyi zla'i steng *//
NG0277:223: rgya gram lte ba nr-i bcas pa //
NG0277:224: a yur+dz+nya na bin du b+h+rum //
NG0277:225: shin tu gsal bar shes par bya'o //
NG0277:226: hu~m pad+ma stong ldan dbus kyi pho brang nas //
NG0277:227: bcom ldan gsung mchog mgon po tshe dpag med //
NG0277:228: thugs ka'i dpal be'u zla gsang ga'u nas //
NG0277:229: rnal 'byor byang chub sems kyi a yuhdmar po 'di //
NG0277:230: rtse gcig bdag gis bsgrubs pa'i tshe lags kyi //
NG0277:231: bdag la byin gyis rlobs shing gshegs su gsol //
NG0277:232: shar phyogs mngon par dga' ba'i zhing khams nas //
NG0277:233: rdo rje rigs kyi yum chen dbyings phyug ma //
NG0277:234: lho phyogs dpal dang ldan pa'i zhing khams nas //
NG0277:235: rin chen rigs kyi yum chen ma ma ki //
NG0277:236: nub phyogs bde ba can gyi zhing khams nas //
NG0277:237: pad+ma rigs kyi yum chen na bza' dkar //
NG0277:238: byang phyogs rnam dag bkod pa'i zhing khams nas //
NG0277:239: las kyi rigs kyi yum chen dam tshig sgrol //
NG0277:240: dbus phyogs byang chub snying po'i zhing khams nas //
NG0277:241: de bzhin rigs kyi yum chen sangs rgyas spyan //
NG0277:242: bde ba rgyas 'debs reg pa sra ba'i sa //
NG0277:243: bde ba tshe 'phel de ni gsher ba'i chu //
NG0277:244: bde ba za byed de ni dro ba'i me //
NG0277:245: bde ba rmongs byed de ni g.yo ba'i rlung *//
NG0277:246: thig le nam mkha' bde stong 'bebs mdzad ma //
NG0277:247: rdo rje tshe yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NG0277:248: rdo rje sgeg mo dga' ba'i ye shes rol //
NG0277:249: rin chen phreng ba ma ni mchog dga' nyid //
NG0277:250: pad+ma klu len dga' bral ye shes sbyong *//
NG0277:251: las kyi karma lhan skyes ye shes spyod //
NG0277:252: rdo rje bdug pa ma ni thig le g.yo //
NG0277:253: rin chen me tog ma ni thig le 'bar //
NG0277:254: pad+ma mar me ma ni thig le'i 'bebs //
NG0277:255: las kyi dri chab ma ni thig le brten //
NG0277:256: byams pa'i lcags kyu mas ni zhi bas 'gugs //
NG0277:257: snying rje zhags pa mas ni rgyas pas 'ching *//
NG0277:258: dga' ba'i lcags sgrog mas ni dbang du sdud //
NG0277:259: btang snyoms dril bu mas ni drag pos 'bebs //
NG0277:260: lha mo nyi shu'i thugs kyi @#//
NG0277:262: rnal 'byor byang chub sems kyi a yuhdmar po 'di //
NG0277:263: rtse gcig bdag gi bsgrubs pa'i tshe lags kyi //
NG0277:264: bdag la byin gyis rlobs shing gshegs su gsol //
NG0277:265: a yur+dz+nya na sa ma ya dza /
NG0277:267: bcom ldan mgon po snang mtha' tshe dpag med //
NG0277:268: sku mdog dmar po gzi brjid 'bar //
NG0277:271: phyogs bcu nam mkha' gang ba'i bgegs bcom nas //
NG0277:272: bcom ldan deng 'dir tshe yi dngos grub stsol //
NG0277:273: 'gro ba yongs kyi tshe la mnga' mdzad kyang *//
NG0277:274: 'gro ba yongs kyi tshe ni mi 'gugs kyis //
NG0277:275: bdag cag rnal 'byor mched lcam 'khor bcas kyi //
NG0277:276: tshe la nyams pa mchis na gso ru gsol //
NG0277:277: tshe la yo ba mchis na bsrang du gsol //
NG0277:278: tshe la ya rab mchis na dgug tu gsol //
NG0277:279: tshe la chad pa mchis na rdo rje'i mdud pa mdzad du gsol //
NG0277:280: shar phyogs dri za'i lag nas tshe khug la //
NG0277:281: shar lho'i me lha'i lag nas drod phyung zhig / lho phyogs gshin rje'i lag nas srog skyobs la //
NG0277:282: lho nub srin po'i lag nas sha rnams khug / nub phyogs klu yi lag nas dpal phrog la //
NG0277:283: nub byang rlung lha'i lag nas dbugs phrog cig /
NG0277:284: byang phyogs gnod sbyin lag nas longs spyod khug /
NG0277:285: byang shar dbang ldan lag nas zungs khrag drongs //
NG0277:286: steng phyogs nyi zla'i lag nas mdangs phrog la //
NG0277:287: 'og phyogs sa bdag lag nas gzi brjid khug / lha dbang brgya byin lag nas srog khug la //
NG0277:288: ma yams dmu srin lag nas tshe drongs shig /
NG0277:289: btsan 'dre btsun 'dre'i lag nas longs spyod khug /
NG0277:290: the'u rang 'gong po'i lag nas srog skyobs shig /
NG0277:291: yul bdag ma srin la gnas dpal khug cig /
NG0277:292: tshe khug srog skyobs bcol pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NG0277:293: om a yur+dz+nya na tshe b+h+rum /
NG0277:294: sra byed sa la dbang byed sangs rgyas spyan //
NG0277:295: mnyen sdud chu la dbang byed ma ma ki //
NG0277:296: sreg byed me yi kun spyod gos dkar mo //
NG0277:297: g.yo byed rlung gi 'gugs byed dam tshig sgrol //
NG0277:298: kun shongs go 'byed nam mkha'i dbyings phyug ma //
NG0277:299: rdo rje sgeg mo bde ba'i nyams la spyod //
NG0277:300: rin chen phreng ba bde ba mi brjed 'dzin //
NG0277:301: pad+ma dbyangs mkhan bde ba'i nyams la rol //
NG0277:302: las kyi gar mkhan bde ba'i 'bebs pa'o //
NG0277:303: bde ba rgyas 'debs zhi ba'i nyams dang ldan //
NG0277:304: bde ba tshe 'phel rgyas las brjid par ldan //
NG0277:305: bde ba za byed rang gi lus la 'bar //
NG0277:306: bde ba rmongs byed rnam par rtog pa 'joms //
NG0277:307: byang chub sesam kyi dud pa'i sprin du 'khrigs //
NG0277:308: rin chen 'dzes pa'i me tog yab la 'bul //
NG0277:309: mar me 'od gsal yab yum 'du 'bral med //
NG0277:310: thig le bdud rtsi yum gyi b+ha gar 'bebs //
NG0277:311: lcags kyus drang pas nyams ni sems la 'char //
NG0277:312: zhags pas bcings pas bde ba lus la @#//
NG0277:314: lcags sgrog sdom pas mthong snang lus la skyes //
NG0277:315: dril bus sgeg pas gsung ni sngags su 'char //
NG0277:316: las bzhi'i phrin las bag chags sems la smin //
NG0277:317: tshe la dbang mdzad lha mo nyi shu yis //
NG0277:318: tshe khug tshe drongs gsang ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NG0277:320: shar gyi phyogs nas tshe 'dren srog 'gugs ma //
NG0277:321: byams pa'i rang bzhin lcags kyu ma //
NG0277:322: phyag g.yas zla ba'i dkyil 'khor bsnams //
NG0277:323: sku mdog dkar po 'od dang ldan //
NG0277:324: phyag g.yon nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bsnams //
NG0277:326: phyag g.yas zla ba'i dkyil steng na //
NG0277:327: thabs kyi tshe 'dzin bum pa bsnams //
NG0277:328: phyag g.yon nyi ma'i dkyil steng na //
NG0277:330: 'gro kun tshe la mnga' brnyes ma //
NG0277:331: tshe khug srog skyobs gsang ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NG0277:333: lho yi phyogs nas srog skyobs tshe 'gugs ma //
NG0277:334: snying rje'i rang bzhin lha mo zhags pa ma //
NG0277:335: sku mdog sngon mo 'bar ba la //
NG0277:337: phyag g.yas zla ba'i gzhal yas nas //
NG0277:338: shes rab tshe yi bum pa bsnams //
NG0277:339: phyag g.yon nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0277:340: thabs kyi tshe 'ching zhags pa bsnams //
NG0277:341: 'gro kun tshe srog sdud mdzad ma //
NG0277:342: rnal 'byor tshe yi las mdzod cig / pa sha
NG0277:343: hu~m / nub kyi phyogs nas srog skyobs tshe 'gugs
NG0277:344: ma // dga' bas dbang mdzad lha mo lcags sgrog ma //
NG0277:345: sku mdog dmar po 'bar ba la //
NG0277:347: phyag g.yas zla ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0277:348: shes rab stong pa'i tshe 'dzin ma //
NG0277:349: phyag g.yon nyi ma'i dkyil steng na //
NG0277:350: thabs kyi lcags sgrog snying rje can //
NG0277:351: khams gsum tshe srog mnga' mdzad ma //
NG0277:352: rnal 'byor tshe la longs spyod kun //
NG0277:353: khug cig drongs shig brtan par mdzod //
NG0277:355: byang gi phyogs nas srog skyobs tshe 'gugs ma //
NG0277:356: btang snyoms rang bzhin lha mo dril bu ma //
NG0277:357: sku mdog ljang gu 'bar ba la //
NG0277:359: phyag g.yas zla ba'i dkyil 'khor na //
NG0277:360: kun gyi tshe 'dzin bum pa bsnams //
NG0277:361: phyag g.yon nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor na //
NG0277:362: kun gyi tshe dgyes dril bu 'khrol //
NG0277:363: 'gro kun tshe la mnga' mdzad kyang *//
NG0277:366: tshe khug srog skyob phrin las mdzod //
NG0277:369: ma lus bum pa'i bcud la bsdu //
NG0277:370: de nas rdo rje'i tshe bcings pa //
NG0277:371: badzra s+pho ta bam zhes pas //
NG0277:373: lcags sgro dag gis bcing bar bya //
NG0277:374: rang nyid lhar gsal sna bug nas //
NG0277:376: om badzra a yu she hum a /
NG0277:377: de bas 'gro drug thams cad kyi //
NG0277:378: tshe dang gzi brjid kun phrogs nas //
NG0277:379: za ma tog tu bsdus nas ni //
NG0277:382: dpa' bo 'bru lnga gsal ba yis //
NG0277:383: tshe yi dbang ni bskur bar gyur //
NG0277:384: om phung po lha yi dkyil 'khor du //
NG0277:385: rgyal ba rigs lnga'i rang bzhin las //
NG0277:386: 'byung lnga yum gyi gzugs su bcas //
NG0277:387: khyod la bskur bas tshe yi dbang *//
NG0277:388: rdo rje tshe dbang thob gyur cig / ka la sha bak+sha a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NG0277:390: de nas slob ma'i snying ga'i nr-i la tshe bstim ste //
NG0277:391: rang lus gzi brjid 'bar te 'od dang ldan //
NG0277:392: khams kyi bdud rtsi rgyas par gyur //
NG0277:393: tshe yi rang bzhin yi ge nr-i //
NG0277:394: skye mched a ru rab tu gnas //
NG0277:395: cis kyang mi tshugs mi shigs pa'i //
NG0277:396: stong pa'i go cha bla na med //
NG0277:397: chos kyi dbyings su sbas nas ni //
NG0277:398: sangs rgyas kyis kyang mi gzigs so //
NG0277:399: de nas gtor ma gtang bar bya //
NG0277:401: spyod lam legs par gnas par bya'o //
NG0277:402: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa 'chi med tshe'i rgyud las */
NG0277:403: tshe bsgrubs pa chen po'i le'u ste bcu pa'o //    // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis /
NG0277:404: gsang ba dag pa'i dkyil 'khor du tshe bsgrub pa 'di gsungs so //
NG0277:405: bde ba'i gnas su dkyil 'khor ni //
NG0277:406: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad gru chad sgo //
NG0277:407: dbus na mgon po tshe dpag med //
NG0277:408: shar na mi bskyod lhor rin 'byung *//
NG0277:409: nub na snang mtha' byang don grub //
NG0277:410: sa yi snying po rdo rje sems //
NG0277:411: nam mkha'i snying po rin chen sems //
NG0277:412: spyan ras gzigs ni pad+ma sems //
NG0277:413: las kyi sems dpa' phyag rdor yin //
NG0277:414: sgo bzhi gshin rje stobs chen dang *//
NG0277:415: rta mgrin bdud rtsi 'khyil pa gnas //
NG0277:416: tshe bum chang dang tshe 'bras bca' //
NG0277:417: mda' dang dar bcas mchod rdzas rnams //
NG0277:418: dkyil 'khor du ni mdzes par bsham //
NG0277:419: bde gshegs bskyed cig spyan drangs bstim //
NG0277:420: mchod nas tshe yi dngos grub bsgrub //
NG0277:421: om ru ru s+phu ru dz+wa la tish+wa sid+d+hi lo
NG0277:422: tsa ni sarba sa ar+tha d+ha na a yur+dz+nya na
NG0277:423: bin du b+h+rum / a pa ri mi ta tshe b+h+rum /
NG0277:424: hu~m dbus kyi mgon po tshe dpag med //
NG0277:425: yab yum thugs kyi ga'u nas //
NG0277:426: a yuhdmar po rang byung nas //
NG0277:427: don grub thugs rgyud rang bzhin bkug / rdzas la bstim zhing bsgrub par bya //
NG0277:428: byang phyogs nub phyogs pad+ma dbang gi dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0277:429: bcom ldan byams mgon tshe dpag med //
NG0277:430: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor zla gsang ga'u nas //
NG0277:431: byang chub sems kyi a yuhdmar po 'di //
NG0277:432: rtse gcig dbang gis bsgrubs pa'i tshe lags na //
NG0277:433: byin gyis brlabs shing bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NG0277:434: rigs kyi rgyal ba yab yum rnams //
NG0277:435: tshul mchog 'di yis shes par bya //
NG0277:436: tshe yi pho nya btang nas kyang *//
NG0277:437: srid gsum gnas nas tshe srog ni //
NG0277:438: yi ge nr-i ru bsdus byas nas //
NG0277:439: byang sems bde ba chen po yi /
NG0277:440: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa nyid //
NG0277:441: a yuhdmar po shes par bya //
NG0277:442: skye ba med pa'i sems nyid 'di //
NG0277:443: 'chi med rdo rje zhes bya ste //
NG0277:444: mi 'gyur g.yung drung ye brdal che //
NG0277:446: nub ye shes rgyal mtshan yin //
NG0277:447: de lta bu yi dngos grub ni //
NG0277:448: rnal 'byor bdag gis blang bar bya //
NG0277:449: mched dang lcam dral slob ma rnams //
NG0277:450: tshe yi bum pas dbang bskur nas //
NG0277:451: tshe yi rang bzhin gnas shes pa //
NG0277:452: dpa' bo 'bru lngas dbang bstim bya //
NG0277:453: mkha' 'gro chos skyong gtor ma gtang *//
NG0277:454: gter sba dge sngo dkyil 'khor bsdu //
NG0277:456: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa 'chi med tshe'i rgyud las /
NG0277:457: gsang ba dag pa'i dkyil 'khor du tshe bsgrub pa'i
NG0277:458: le'u ste bcu gcig pa'o // // de nas bcom
NG0277:459: ldan 'das kyis / gsang ba dag pa'i rdzas la tshe bsgrub pa 'di gsungs so //
NG0277:460: bkra shis dag pa'i rdzas btsal te //
NG0277:461: mdo sde zangs gzhong 'khar sder du //
NG0277:462: kr-i ya nya phyis dung chos la //
NG0277:463: ma ha skye ba bdun pa'i ro //
NG0277:464: bya rgod rkang gi sbubs bltas te //
NG0277:465: zhun chen mar mer gzugs bdun pa //
NG0277:466: skra kham shel mig dpral dbyibs che //
NG0277:467: sme bdun ba spu zang thal byung *//
NG0277:468: dung so 'khor bar yod pa yis //
NG0277:469: tshe skyems tshe 'bras gzungs thag bzung *//
NG0277:470: snod ni gzhal yas khang gyur nas //
NG0277:471: tshe skyems sid+d+ha lo tsa ni //
NG0277:472: ljang ser gzhal gcig phyag bzhi ma //
NG0277:473: tshe dar gri gug g.yas pa na //
NG0277:474: bdud rtsi bum pa rgya gram g.yon //
NG0277:475: de yi mkha' dbyings tshe dpag med //
NG0277:476: dmar po gzhal gcig phyag bzhi pa //
NG0277:477: rin chen phreng ba za ma tog / shel phreng ne'u le'i rkyal pa g.yon //
NG0277:478: de 'khor rigs kyi yum chen lnga //
NG0277:479: rigs mdog yum chen lnga ni phyag mtshan rigs //
NG0277:480: mig la rgyas 'debs lcags kyu dkar //
NG0277:481: rna bar rmongs byed zhags pa sngo //
NG0277:482: sna la tshe 'phel lcags sgrog dmar //
NG0277:483: lce la za byed dril bu ljang *//
NG0277:485: dmar po pad+ma rgya gram bsnams //
NG0277:486: a yuhtshe b+h+rum dz+nya na tshe b+h+rum bin du b+h+rum /
NG0277:487: a pa ra mi ta tshe b+h+rum /
NG0277:488: chag pa'i rdo rje bdag nyid che //
NG0277:489: pad+ma rgyal po kun d+ha li //
NG0277:490: sprul pa'i khro bo grangs med pas //
NG0277:491: tshe la gnod pa'i bgegs rnams kun //
NG0277:492: de yi gzugs bcom pha rol du //
NG0277:493: song zhing tshe la gnod byed bskrad //
NG0277:495: tshe la dbang bskur bstim pa dang *//
NG0277:496: sbas nas rgyas btab smon lam gdab //
NG0277:497: thod pa longs spyod gter du bcangs //
NG0277:498: sha rnams su yis zos pas ni //
NG0277:499: thun mong dngos grub thob par 'gyur //
NG0277:500: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa 'chi med tshe'i rgyud las /
NG0277:501: gsang ba dag pa'i rdzas las /
NG0277:502: tshe bsgrub pa'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa'o ///
NG0277:504: mkha' dbyings rnam par dag pa'i yum la tshe bsgrub pa'i cho ga 'di gsungs so //
NG0277:505: dben pa'i gnas su phyin nas ni //
NG0277:506: pad+ma can nam dung can nam //
NG0277:508: mtshan dang ldan pa'i gzungs ma la //
NG0277:509: dpa' bo 'bru lnga lus la bkod //
NG0277:510: rigs lnga ye shes lngar byin brlabs //
NG0277:511: yab yum mkha' gsang bsnol bas ni //
NG0277:514: bde mchog bde bral bde ba dang *//
NG0277:516: hrihlas rta mgrin khro bo dmar //
NG0277:517: zhal gsum pa la phyag drug pa //
NG0277:518: sngags 'chang rgyal po gang gnas pa //
NG0277:519: phyag rgya'i bdag nyid de la gnas //
NG0277:520: phyag rgya chen po'i dkyil 'khor na //
NG0277:521: sma sha nag mo don snying za //
NG0277:522: de yi yang gsang thugs dkyil nas //
NG0277:523: gsung gi rgyal po rta mchog dpal //
NG0277:524: phyag mtshan phyag na 'brug drug bsnams //
NG0277:528: glog gi kha nas thog 'bebs la //
NG0277:529: gnod sbyin dmar po'i klad pa 'gems //
NG0277:530: de yis sems kyi dal bsnams nas //
NG0277:531: drongs shig drongs shig tshe drongs shig / rdo rje tshe yi dngos grub stsol //
NG0277:532: om a yur+dz+nya na tshe b+h+rum /
NG0277:533: dga' ba bzhi dang ldan pa yi //
NG0277:534: bsnyen bsgrub rnam bzhi bsgrub pa yis //
NG0277:535: khu ba 'thung na nad med cing *//
NG0277:536: de yi tshe yang lha dang mnyam //
NG0277:537: dbang gi mchog tu de 'gyur ro //
NG0277:538: sgrub pa po yi thugs gnas bstim //
NG0277:540: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa 'chi med tshe'i rgyud las /
NG0277:541: gsang ba mkha' dbyings la tshe bsgrub pa'i le'u ste bcu gsum pa'o ///
NG0277:542: / de nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rdo rje chos kyis /
NG0277:543: mchod pa de kho na nyid kyis mchod nas /
NG0277:545: sangs rgyas bde ba chen po'i thugs //
NG0277:546: 'gro ba kun la kun gzhi yid //
NG0277:547: rnal 'byor a yuh'i tshe rnams bsgrub //
NG0277:548: dam rdzas byang sems dkar dmar len //
NG0277:549: 'di yi tshe dang srog brten nas //
NG0277:550: mgon po khyed la rjes yi rang *//
NG0277:552: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis 'di gsungs so //
NG0277:553: 'gyur med tshe yi dngos grub rgyud //
NG0277:554: rdo rje chos kyis zung la mkha' 'gros srungs //
NG0277:555: chos kyi spyan ldan spyod pas 'gro don mdzad //
NG0277:556: mi nub bstan pa rgyas par khyed kyis spyod //
NG0277:558: ston pa dang 'khor rnams chos nyid kyi ngang du thim ste chos skur bzhugs so //
NG0277:559: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa 'chi med tshe'i rgyud las /
NG0277:560: rgyud gtad pa'i le'u ste bcu bzhi pa'o //
NG0277:561: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa 'chi med tshe'i rgyud ces bya
NG0277:562: ba rdzogs so // // rgya gar gyi mkhan po
NG0277:563: pan+dita bi ma la mi tra la /
